requirements:
python3
python3-serial
python3-bitstring

to run:
python3 bridge.py

bridge --
    This is the process(s) to handle communications with the IM.  It is
    actually a collection of servies that communicate with each using
    pipes.  There are 4 main services: model, io, network, and event.


